          "type": "text",
          "text": "The function accepts one or more input parameters that represent the attributes of an energy source. These parameters are used to evaluate whether the energy source meets the criteria for validity. The specific parameters are not provided, but they include attributes like energy source type, capacity, or regulatory compliance status."
